      "title": "Onward Toward Your Trial",
    },
    {
      "completionNpc": null,
      "description": "To obtain the Sword of Trial, you must carry out a task for Trader Simplon. Fight the tracker skeletons in the Ruins of Agony and return with 10 of their rusted swords.\\n",
